## 5. raw#10 honest C3

1. **dupilumab Dupixent 2017** = first FDA biologic AD adult — IL-4Rα dual block IL-4/IL-13. 2019 12-17 → 2022 6+ → 2024 6+ months SC. AD systemic biologic era 시작. quantum-VQE 의 IL-4Rα Fab 가 직접 fit.
2. **nemolizumab Nemluvio 2024** = first FDA IL-31Rα — prurigo nodularis + AD. IL-31 = 만성 가려움 핵심 cytokine. quantum-VQE 의 IL-31Rα Fab pocket leverage.
3. **lebrikizumab Ebglyss 2024** = IL-13 selective second (tralokinumab Adbry 2021 first). IL-13 only block 가 IL-4Rα dual block (dupilumab) 와 efficacy/safety profile 차이. quantum-VQE 의 IL-13 selective Fab pocket.
4. **abrocitinib + upadacitinib 2022 AD** = JAK1 selective oral AD paradigm. tofacitinib pan-JAK 보다 selectivity 높음. baricitinib JAK1/2 EU/JP 만 — US AD 미승인 (FDA black box VTE/MACE concern).
5. **ruxolitinib Opzelura cream 2021** = first topical JAK — AD 12+ + vitiligo 2022. delgocitinib Anzupgo 2024 EU = first topical pan-JAK chronic hand eczema EU. topical JAK 가 systemic JAK 보다 BBW 회피.
6. **tapinarof Vtama 2022 → 2024 AD** = first AhR agonist topical. 2022 psoriasis → 2024 AD 2+. coal-tar mechanism 의 modern reincarnation. quantum-VQE 의 AhR ligand pocket fit.
7. **roflumilast Zoryve 2024 AD** = topical PDE4 expansion (psoriasis 2022 → AD 6+ 2024). crisaborole Eucrisa 2016 first topical PDE4 mild-moderate. cAMP signaling restoration topical.
8. **atopic march** = AD → asthma → 알레르기 progression. 영유아 AD 가 후속 asthma + food allergy + allergic rhinitis 위험인자. dupilumab early intervention 연구 (cross-pulmonology + allergy_immunodef).
9. **pediatric AD + dupilumab 6+ 6-month** = 2022 6+ → 2024 6+ months SC. 발달 + 안전 monitoring 한정. 영유아 임상 + 청소년 임신부 안전 framework gap (cross-adolescent + newborn_perinatal + women_obgyn).
10. **wet-lab + clinical RCT 없음** — quantum-only in-silico, AD 임상 의미 한정. 한국 K-AD 임상 + 식약처 framework 적용 한정.

